name: Ruthless Kitty
description: Say “Hello” to Your New Best Friend Introducing Ruthless Kitty – the cat who gives zero fluffs! Unapologetically un-neutered, this feline renegade isn’t your average tabby. He’s clawed his way through the wild world of crypto, conquering the gnarliest challenges with a ferocity that would make a tiger blush. Ruthless Kitty doesn’t just walk the walk, he struts it.
